## Proposed Changes

### 1. Fix WeatherMap Z-Index

**Current hierarchy (from tasks/fix-ui-overlapping-issues.md):**
- z-10: Widget content
- z-20: Save indicator
- z-30: WeatherMap search controls
- z-40: AI Terminal button + panel
- z-50+: Modals

**Problem:** WeatherMap widget container may have z-index that conflicts

**Solution Options:**
- **Option A:** Set WeatherMap container to z-10 (base widget level)
- **Option B:** Find specific map control with high z-index and reduce it
- **Option C:** Increase AI Terminal panel to z-50 (modal level)

**Recommendation:** Option A - WeatherMap should be z-10 (widget level)

### 2. Remove Minimize Button

**Current:** AI Terminal header likely has two buttons:
```tsx
<div className="header">
  <button onClick={minimize}>Minimize</button>
  <button onClick={close}>Close (X)</button>
</div>
```

**Desired:** Only close button (which minimizes):
```tsx
<div className="header">
  <button onClick={close}>Close (X)</button>
</div>
```

**Verify:** Ensure `close` function in useTerminalStore minimizes (doesn't destroy)

